<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Draft Entry</div>
<dl id="bd7y"> <dt><a href="../../flex/b/bd7.htm">I.2&sect;3.7+</a> </dt> <dd> Late revision for the ballad, contained in an undated letter from Joyce to Sylvia Beach (see Letters, I, <a name="sbApr1927" href="../../FF/fbiog/fwlett.htm#sbApr1927">N.D. 1927</a>). This addition, which arrived too late for inclusion in <cite>transition 2</cite>, does not appear in any subsequent draft; probably early May 1927. <ul><li>MS: Buffalo X.C.127 </li><li>JJA 45 (Book I Chapters 2 and 3): not reproduced. </li><li>Notebooks used: <a name="n26" href="../../FF/fdra/fnbdetails.htm#n26">N26 (VI.B.18)</a> </li></ul> </dd> </dl>
